reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The cord is SOOOO long. I have an iPhone XR so the battery life is abysmal at this point. I love that I can charge my phone and I'm not restricted to a short cable. It charges my phone quickly too. If you use your phone in bed, mindlessly scrolling social media, (no judgment here) the long cable is a lifesaver.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Wish they charged a little faster
reviews.reviewText: This was a replacement to a previous purchase that went kaput. I have an iPhone 14 max plus and have to have a long charging cord due to the furniture vs outlets situation. I had a 6+’ cord for a few years that finally died. I replaced it with a brand I was unfamiliar with and they only lasted a few months so I bought these. I like the fact that it is a fabric type cord instead of a plastic type. It seems to be sturdier. I have noticed that it doesn’t charge as quickly as my original cord even though I have it plugged into a lightening adapter but it doesn’t crawl so I am ok with it. I do like the fact that there are 3 in the pack so I don’t have to keep moving them around. The colors are nice too. And the price was right on. Overall I am pleased with my purchase.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars worked for like 2 months then stopped
reviews.reviewText: Just don’t buy these. Amazon has a million others to choose from. These worked great for two months then one completely failed and one kept giving me a “liquid detected in charging port” pop-up on my phone. When I switched to another charger, the pop-up didn’t show. The length and angle are cool but I would not purchase again.

reviews.reviewText: I just received this a couple of days ago. So far I love it! I will see how long it holds up. Most charger wires short out right up by where it plugs into your phone, so I’m hoping with the side mount it will not get damaged. So far I would highly recommend it but it has only been a few days and I don’t know how long it will last.
